{
  "stem": "812.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And it was-- I don't remember how-- how long a-- a trip it was, but it was winter.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "As I said, it was February.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "It was bitter cold when we arrived in-- at our destination, Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And there we were met by the Gestapo, the SS.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "I remember them with their high black boots, rifles by their sides, and German shepherds.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "These German shepherds were trained to attack, I learned later, only people in civilian clothing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And the SS had a good time threatening us with their rifles and with their dogs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "I was just nine years old, cold, frightened, and no taller than the height of-- of-- of the-- the boots that the Germans wore, the SS wore.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And my brother was always very protective of me, and he would stand by my side.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And we-- I was always very grateful that he was there for me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we walked from the station of Bergen-Belsen to the camp itself.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There-- ah, I need a tissue.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Thank you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "We-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] the-- the barracks, well, the camp itself was surrounded by electrified barbed wire, and [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] there were high guard houses in various parts of-- surrounding the-- the camp.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] whenever it got dark at night, there were searchlights from the guard houses constantly roaming the camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was a very frightening, overwhelming situation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "The barracks were built initially [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] during the First World War in 1917, 1918, meant for just 100 soldiers at the time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "We were with 600 in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "There were triple-decker beds, bunks, with two people in one bunk.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
